songs.title: The Right Stuff (Cover)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: All & Camila & Lauren & Dinah & (Normani) & {Ally}]
Oh nooo
Uh huh
The right stuff
Oh uuuh
(Wow)
{Yeah}
The right stuff


[Verse 1: Lauren & Normani & Camila]
First time was a great time
Second time was a blast
Third time I fell in love
Now I hope it lasts
I can see it in your walk
Love it when you talk
See it in everything you do
Even in your thoughts
You got the right stuff, baby
Love the way you turn me on
You got the right stuff, baby
You're the reason why I sing this song

[Pre-Chorus: Ally & Dinah & (All)]
All that I needed was you (All that I needed)
Oh boy, you're so right
All that I wanted was you
You made all my dreams come true

[Chorus: All & (Normani) & Dinah & {Ally}]
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh (Oh yeah)
Oh, oh, oh, oh (Oooh)
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh
The right stuff
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh {Oh oooh}
Oh, oh, oh, oh {Oh oooh}
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh
The right stuff
